Name: Pacific Liberation Force
About the game: Are you ready to take up arms against El Presidente and his forces of evil? Taking place in a fully destructible environment, complete 18 challenging, trigger happy and arcade-like missions! You'll be conducting aerial warfare versus a wide range of enemies, from simple footsoldiers to heavily armed tanks and from fighter jets to incredible carriers! Push your heli's to the limit if you want to stand a chance! During the action packed missions you will have to protect and destroy objectives: beware when you open fire because everything you see can be blown up including whole villages! Features: - Fully destructible environment with intense, explosive visual effects ! - Fast paced action with fluid and intuitive gameplay ! - More than 16 story based single player missions !
